<div3 id="Selection-def" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
<head>Selection</head>
<p> Processing instructions for general purpose content selection or filtering.
		Content may be conditionally included or excluded based on the evaluation of the  <loc href="http://www.w3.org/TR/di-gloss/#def-delivery-context-v2" xlink:actuate="onRequest" xlink:show="replace">
				delivery context
			</loc>.
		This may include capabilities of the requesting device, the user's profile (e.g. age, preferences),
		the user's context (e.g. location) and any dynamic factors (e.g. battery life, the transport bandwidth).
		A selection criterion is represented by the value of the sel:expr attribute.
		This module is based son elements and attributes from the <loc href="http://www.w3.org/TR/cselection/" xlink:actuate="onRequest" xlink:show="replace">DISelect</loc> specification. 
		</p>
